Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就只有用坚决不暴露的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效仿贤者了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话   我有一个好的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立少爷的影武者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是影武者嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 望
